Author: OkieNope
Text: The last time I ate cheesecake was last summer at my cousin's wedding and it gave me the worst headache ever :/ I think it's due to all the sugar, plus I hadn't eaten Cheesecake in a long long time. As a kid I would eat it any chance I got lol. Now I would just have vegan cheesecake if I really wanted it again but im too afraid to try it out yet
